ildren":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2178416778","tinyui":"/x/igDYgQ","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2178416778","webui":"/spaces/BAN/overview","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2178416778"}},{"id":"2316959745","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2316959745","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjMxNjk1OTc0NQ==","status":"current","title":"TMP","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":887957284},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2316959745/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2316959745/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2316959745/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2316959745/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2316959745","tinyui":"/x/AQAaig","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2316959745","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2316959745/TMP","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2316959745"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<h1>Post producci&oacute;n</h1><ul><li><p>Comentarios en <a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-pix-service/pull/18\">https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-pix-service/pull/18</a></p></li><li><p>Revisar current_commerce en pix_portal. Uso de sesi&oacute;n compartida con commerce-suite. Ver PR <a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-pix-portal/pull/8#discussion_r1553901345\">https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-pix-portal/pull/8#discussion_r1553901345</a> </p></li><li><p>Cachear nombre de cajero y nombre de sucursal en pix-service. Usar Dory o algun mecanismo de cacheo.</p></li><li><p>guardar en el commerce_branch_info el branch_code y el commerce_code</p></li><li><p>Dockerfile local: instlar default-mysql-client para poder correr el comando <code>rails dbconsole</code></p></li><li><p>Cuando un usuario cambia de comercio en el portal de comercios, en el portal de pix se requiere un full reload para ver el cambio de comercio. Navegaci&oacute;n con turbo no actualiza el comercio en la vista del perfil del usuario.</p></li><li><p>Cache en pix-portal para los before_action del application controller. Demora mucho en obtener la current branch, chequear permisos, etc</p></li><li><p>Mecanismo backup para creaci&oacute;n de payments. No confiar unicamente en los webhooks. </p></li><li><p>cambiar ruta de voucher para que use hook_alias en lugar del payment_id. considerando que la relaci&oacute;n es uno a uno entre hook y payment. desarrollar endpoint get_payment_by_hook_alias.</p></li><li><p>ErrorsController en pix-portal. Hacer que herede de <code>ActionController::Base</code> para evitar que salte algun error en los filtros de ActionController presentes en el ApplicationController. (Gasti: ya empec&eacute; a verlo, dej&eacute; las pruebas por la mitad) Ver branch <a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-pix-portal/tree/fix-errors-controller\">fix-errors-controller</a></p></li><li><p>Implementar en pix-service un mecanismo similar al de pix-portal para mostrar los errores 500 (<code>config.exceptions_app = self.routes</code>) con las rutas y un ErrorsController, para mostrar un JSON generico como el de angus para los InternalServerError.</p></li></ul>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/3005153322"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":791369337},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3005153322/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3005153322/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3005153322/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3005153322/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3005153322","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3005153322/Deuda+tecnica+PIX","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3005153322","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3005153322","tinyui":"/x/KgAfsw","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}